    "causal_summary": "The sk-code-review README is a tabular reference card with stray non-numbered headings (`## Findings`, `## Review Context`) breaking the section sequence, and it documents the output contract wrong: it shows `## Findings` before `## Code Review Summary`, invents a `## Review Context` heading that does not exist, and omits the mandatory `Review status:` final line that downstream automation parses",
